results.title: Silent voices
results.brief_description: Broken into three segments entitled ‘The Rape’, ‘The Miscarriage’ and ‘The Dream’, this expressionist animation poignantly conveys the emotional trauma experienced by a young woman who is sexually abused by her tyrannical father. A more fully realised version of ‘deCollage’ a shorter film by the same director

results.title: Shift
results.brief_description: Set amongst bleak futuristic cityscapes this film combines live action with 2D and 3D computer animation. After experiencing problems with his vision Travis gradually finds it impossible to distinguish reality from his hallucinations about getting back to nature. Is someone controlling his mind?

results.title: Penguins off the page
results.brief_description: A biology teacher struggles to make his students pay attention to his lesson on different species of penguins. Little does he know that the very penguins he is discussing have come to life on his desktop, providing an amusing performance that brings his words to life. A plasticine animation in a live action classroom.
